data.description: Discover your dream home on this spacious 1.25-acre lot. This fantastic property was recently renovated in February 2023, complete with a brand-new roof. The kitchen features modern cabinets, sleek countertops, and stainless steel appliances, while the main living area is filled with natural light. The bathrooms have been updated with new vanities and refreshed baths and showers. The primary bedroom has an ensuite bathroom, and the other bedrooms offer flexibility. Throughout the open floor plan home, fresh paint and updated lighting create a welcoming atmosphere. Step onto the enclosed patio, leading to the private backyard. Don't miss this incredible opportunity!
